  "prompt": "Which is the best modular kitchen in india?",
  "response": "The \"best\" modular kitchen in India can vary depending on individual preferences, budget, and requirements such as space, design style, and functionality. However, several brands are well-regarded for their quality, design, and customer service. Some of the top modular kitchen brands in India include:\n\n1. **H\u00e4fele**: Known for its fittings and hardware, H\u00e4fele also offers high-quality modular kitchen solutions with a focus on innovative designs and functionality.\n\n2. **Sleek by Asian Paints**: This brand provides a range of customizable options with modern designs and efficient space utilization.\n\n3. **Godrej Interio**: Godrej is a trusted brand in India, offering durable and stylish modular kitchen solutions that cater to a variety of tastes and budgets.\n\n4. **Hettich**: Renowned for their advanced hardware and fittings, Hettich's modular kitchens emphasize durability and ergonomic design.\n\n5. **Nolte**: A premium German brand that offers sophisticated designs, Nolte Kitchens are known for their quality materials and contemporary aesthetics.\n\n6. **W\u00fcrfel K\u00fcche**: W\u00fcrfel emphasizes European styling and precision engineering, offering high-quality materials and finishes.\n\n7. **Livspace**: As an interior design and renovation platform, Livspace provides end-to-end solutions for modular kitchens, tailored to specific needs and preferences.\n\n8. **Bonito Designs**: This company offers personalized interior solutions, including modular kitchens that focus on maximizing space and utility.\n\nWhen selecting a modular kitchen provider, consider factors such as design flexibility, material quality, warranty, after-sales service, and overall value for money. Visiting showrooms or consulting with designers can also help in making an informed decision.",
